    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Sunnybank.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Sunnybank?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Sunnybank values are driven by the suburb's distinct community character and food precinct, Pacific Motorway access, proximity to Garden City in Upper Mount Gravatt, and the genuine depth of demand from both family owner-occupiers and investors. The suburb's multicultural buyer pool is broad and consistent, and properties that present well and sit in good street positions attract competition from multiple buyer types simultaneously. School catchments add a further layer of appeal for families with children.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Sunnybank?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Sunnybank homes typically sell within 25 to 38 days. The suburb's broad buyer pool, which spans local families, interstate buyers, and investors from across Brisbane's southern corridor, means that correctly priced properties attract genuine inquiry from multiple directions. Buyers who target Sunnybank tend to act with confidence when a property meets their criteria, and a campaign that communicates the address's specific advantages clearly tends to accelerate that decision-making.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Sunnybank?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Sunnybank offers a lively multicultural lifestyle about thirteen kilometres south of the Brisbane CBD. The food precinct is the suburb's most celebrated feature, with a concentration of Asian restaurants, fresh produce markets, and specialty food retailers that makes everyday living here genuinely different from comparable southern Brisbane suburbs. Garden City in Upper Mount Gravatt provides major retail access, and Pacific Motorway access makes the CBD and Gold Coast a practical commute from this address.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Sunnybank a good suburb to invest in?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Sunnybank has consistently attracted investor interest for its combination of strong rental demand, a deep and diverse buyer pool at resale, and a suburb identity that is genuinely difficult to replicate elsewhere in the southern corridor. The suburb's community character, food precinct, and motorway access create a tenant profile that values this specific address. Investors who understand the driver of demand here make better decisions about property selection, preparation, and positioning.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

